This isn't easy work, but you're
showing up.

6
00:00:09,491 --> 00:00:10,698
That matters.

7
00:00:10,948 --> 00:00:13,270
I'm Cassandra, you coach for today.

8
00:00:13,420 --> 00:00:16,346
And today's Stoppr lesson is
a real-life one.

9
00:00:16,496 --> 00:00:18,307
One you've probably lived through.

10
00:00:18,557 --> 00:00:20,322
Let's talk about peer pressure.

11
00:00:20,472 --> 00:00:21,447
And sugar.

12
00:00:21,836 --> 00:00:22,858
You're at a dinner.

13
00:00:23,008 --> 00:00:24,494
Maybe it's friends.

14
00:00:24,644 --> 00:00:25,898
Maybe family.

15
00:00:26,048 --> 00:00:29,159
The meal is done, and then—here
it comes.

16
